Titolo: Avenger (1981 video game)

Anno: 1981

Descrizione: Avenger is a Space Invaders clone published on cartridge by Commodore in 1981 for the VIC-20. The game uses multicolor graphics and supports keyboard or joystick control. The player starts with 3 bases (lives) and gets new base at 1500 points.A year later it was released for the Commodore 64.